title: Cli improvements
body:
- [x] No temporary file when editing/adding a recipe
- [x] Select last owner used
- [x] Select last model used

The owner and model are stored in `$DROPIN_ROOT/config.toml`

title: Fix CLI: owner change
body: The model is now deselected when the owner is changed

title: Structure history
body: This branch contains some work on `dropin-compiler`. The pull request #20 replaces this crate with `dropin-bootstrap`. It will compile `syntaxes` and `modules` and everything else will be described in our langage. That's why we won't need `dropin-compiler` anymore, so this PR is merged for historical purposes.
